name: The Burger Barn
comment: Great burger place-LGBTQ-friendly.

name: Mag Cafè

comment: There are three steps that go down into the sink area and then you must go up when entering the stall. Bring a permanent marker with you to add to the bathroom graffiti art.

name: Gecko's Pub
directions: Left of the bar and just right of the kitchen entrance.

name: Brighton Women's Centre drop in
comment: http://www.womenscentre.org.uk/index.php?What_We_Do:Drop_In_Service

Friday mornings 10.30am to 12.30pm.

name: Church of the Beatitudes, United Church of Christ
directions: Enter through the office during business hours - 9:30am-3:30pm Monday-Thursday and 9am-12:30 on Friday. Ask receptionist for directions to restroom.
comment: All are welcome!

name: University of Brighton Grand Parade building
comment: This building is open to the public. You don't have to spend anything or be connected to the university to use this toilet.

name: Jubilee Library
directions: When you come in the main entrance, go to the far wall and bear left to find the the women's room and the men's room. There are a few unisex accessible toilets (one with babychange) by the children's section. I think there are toilets on the other floors, accessible by stairs or lift.
comment: This is a public library. There's no need to be a member or buy anything to use these toilets.

name: Friend's Meeting House
directions:
When you come in the main entrance, the gendered toilets are on your right. There are steps into the main entrance. The corridoor leading to the toilets is sloped with a handrail.

The step-free entrance is on the left when you are facing the building. I've not used this door so I can't describe how to get to the accessible unisex toilet from there.
comment:
They ask you to make a small donation after using the loo if you've come in off the street.

The lock on the accessible loo is difficult to work.

name: The Basement
directions: The entrance is at street level but the venue is in the basement. There is a lift. It's small so you won't have trouble seeing the toilets.

name: Wellness Services Inc
directions: Entry off of 4th across the street from the YWCA.
comment: Just ask to use the restroom.

name: The Paint Spot

name: Secret Sandwich  Society

name: Spellbinder Bookstord
